    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i guess i get what you mean about self care but it feels like more than just needing a break. it feels more like... the damage is just permanent. like there's no version of me that doesn't have these cracks in it. do you think it's possible for someone to just be too far gone to actually be okay again?",
